# drop columns that we don't think will be useful
df["goal"] = df["goal"] * df["static_usd_rate"]
df["isUS"] = df["country"].apply(lambda c: 1 if c == "US" else 0).astype("category")
df["pledge_per_backer"] = df["usd_pledged"] / df["backers_count"]
df = df[df["state"] != "live"]
